</paragraph>
<paragraph id="215A368EEB438B054CA440A7FD0CFF7E" blockId="4.[136,679,159,217]" box="[136,679,159,181]" pageId="4" pageNumber="298">
‘Cido Ada’— 
<bibRefCitation id="45744B7FEB438B054D2740A7FE24FF7E" author="Tics, A." box="[267,399,159,181]" pageId="4" pageNumber="298" refId="ref5823" refString="Tics, A. (2000) Ziemelu citrons Cido. Jauna auglu kultura. [author's edition], [Pure], 257 pp." type="book" year="2000">Tīcs 2000: 37</bibRefCitation>
